# Security Headers Configuration
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
  X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data: https://www.google-analytics.com; connect-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com; frame-ancestors 'none';